# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if delegates have different models/operating systems
#   you may want to skip locking for packages and rely on exact versions in setup.py
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similarly, the recommended best practice is to check poetry.lock into version control.
#poetry.lock

